Razavi-Bench License

Razavi-Bench is derived from Behzad Razavi's "Analog Design Experiments With
AI--Part 1 [The Analog Mind]" and "Analog Design Experiments With AI--Part 2
[The Analog Mind]", published in IEEE Solid-State Circuits Magazine.

The benchmark questions and related source materials are included or adapted
with permission from Behzad Razavi. Original article, question, and figure
copyrights remain with their respective rights holders, including Behzad Razavi
and/or IEEE, as applicable.

